Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,ProSeka AfterTalk: Colors of Pure Sense Edition
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:02.02,Default,host,0,0,0,,Hello, everyone. Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:05.92,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I'm Suzuki Minori, the voice of Ena Shinonome from Nightcord at 25:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:13.26,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,In this ProSeka AfterTalk, we'll look back on the event while reading the messages you've sent in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:16.76,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Today's episode covers the Colors of Pure Sense event.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:20.28,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I hope you all enjoyed the story!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:22.12,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:25.84,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Between the Thanksgiving event and the stage greetings for the movie,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:30.54,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,things have been quite busy with real-life cast events lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:35.16,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,And then this Niigo event, Ena's story event, started right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:42.62,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's been a whirlwind for everyone, but I hope you've been enjoying it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:49.44,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We previously asked for messages for this AfterTalk via the official ProSeka Discord and email.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:52.88,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you all for writing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:56.04,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I honestly wish the staff would let me sneak a peek at every single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:58.86,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I'm really curious to hear what you all thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:03.58,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I'll be sharing some of those messages during the show,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:04.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,so please look forward to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:11.54,Default,host,0,0,0,,Also, please post your thoughts on the event or this stream using the hashtag #ProSekaAfterTalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:14.42,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm also keeping an eye on the YouTube chat,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:17.90,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,so I'll be picking out comments that catch my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:18.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:19.51,Default,host,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:22.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,I see comments like "It was a great story."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:24.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,And people saying "Kon-Niigo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:25.60,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Kon-Niigo to you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:30.80,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Also, we have the AfterLive starting at 10:00 PM,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:36.98,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,and the 3DMV for this event will be released at 10:05 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:40.16,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I'd love to watch those together with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:48.38,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I want to make sure we stay on schedule, but I also want to spend a good amount of time on the story video.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:53.84,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I was a bit selfish and asked to make the story segment longer than usual,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:56.72,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,so I hope you'll stick around and watch it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:12:03.88,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Now, let's start talking about the story
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.88,0:12:05.76,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,for Colors of Pure Sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:09.02,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,What did you all think of this story?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:13.96,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Let's look back on it together while I read your messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:19.46,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,This is actually my first time doing the renewed version of ProSeka AfterTalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:22.98,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It's been about a year, and back then it was the old format.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:32.02,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,So, I'm really happy to be weaving this show together using your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:35.18,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,This first message is from Amelia Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:36.78,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"This is my first time sending in my thoughts."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:37.80,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:43.76,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"The scene that left the biggest impression on me was when Ena deleted her selfie account."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:50.24,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I felt her growth when she, who used to run away from her art, finally decided to face it head-on."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:55.88,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Like Ena, I was also afraid to face myself and kept running away,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:13:00.72,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"but seeing Ena's positive attitude gave me a push, and I want to try my best too."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:02.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,"Suzuki-san, what kind of feelings"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:07.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,"did you put into your performance of Ena this time?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:10.52,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you for the wonderful message.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:11.41,Default,host,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:17.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,Amelia Time, that was a lovely letter. Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:26.22,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'll talk more about this while we watch the story later, but regarding Ena this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:31.66,Default,host,0,0,0,,and also when singing recent Niigo songs, there's something I've been conscious of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:49.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,As her voice actress, I personally tell myself, "I won't let her go back to the old Ena."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:14:04.74,Default,host,0,0,0,,Even if it's slow, Ena is moving forward bit by bit. Because of the nature of Niigo's music, the lyrics can often be quite pessimistic,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:08.78,Default,host,0,0,0,,and the songs themselves have a certain heavy atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:16.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,But I try not to let her get pulled too far into that. Honestly, as a song or a performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:24.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,adding a hint of tears or a negative nuance might make it more striking to the listener,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:28.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,or make people think, "Oh, I love the way she delivered that phrase."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:33.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,There are definitely parts that catch your ear because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:38.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,But I realized that's just my own desire for validation as an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:48.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,I want to make sure I put the fact that Ena is looking forward, even if just a little, into her songs and lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:55.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,So even with the same words, I try to deliver them so you can feel her progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:15:06.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,I've been gradually increasing that sense of positivity based on the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:08.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,That's what I've been keeping in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:11.76,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,while playing her this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:12.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:13.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:19.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,In this event and in recent songs, she's not as cynical about things anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:23.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,I think Ena now truly understands that the world is warmer than she thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:28.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,and that the people around her are there to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:31.68,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I made sure to reflect that in my performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:35.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,Now, moving on,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:39.30,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I'll read one more message.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:43.10,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,This one is from Sudachi Udon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,"Minori-san, good evening."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,Yes, good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.24,0:15:48.98,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I've finished reading Colors of Pure Sense."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:50.10,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:58.32,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"The scene that stuck with me was in Episode 7, where Ena gets so excited because she's having so much fun drawing."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:16:06.36,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Ena, who could only boost her self-esteem through others' praise on her selfie account, finally realized she's fine just as she is."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:11.00,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I realized that my world and my expression can be as free as I want them to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:22.02,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,and as Ena's world gradually gained color and her eyes sparkled with the joy of painting, I could really feel it through your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:23.32,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It moved me to tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:30.34,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I want to keep watching over and supporting Ena as she resolves to never give up on her art and her dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:34.84,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Minori-san, "the color of Ena's heart"... what a beautiful way to put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:39.92,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for bringing that to life so vividly through your performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:41.80,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you for that message.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:44.68,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,And thank you for taking those feelings to heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.24,0:16:53.04,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I always think about how I want Ena's heart to reach everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:58.74,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Of course, she's a game character, a 2D existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:02.40,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,but Ena is truly alive, and well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:06.90,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,No one knows what the future holds for her yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:09.52,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,So, how should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:15.28,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I really want to deliver something that feels raw and real.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:18.28,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I'm so happy to hear your thoughts. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:19.53,Default,host,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:21.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,Moving on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:28.95,Default,host,0,0,0,,There's so much I want to talk about while watching the story, so if I get too carried away now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:29.53,Default,host,0,0,0,,well,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:32.30,Default,host,0,0,0,,five minutes will pass in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:34.40,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,So let's keep things moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:39.88,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I've picked out some scenes that I personally want to talk about,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:41.46,Default,host,0,0,0,,so let's watch them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:44.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,I was a bit selfish with my choices today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:48.02,Default,host,0,0,0,,The staff are shaking their heads like "no, you weren't," but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:48.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,well,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:50.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,I really struggled to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:54.81,Default,host,0,0,0,,I felt like I could just watch from Episode 1 to 8 with you all,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:55.41,Default,host,0,0,0,,but
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:18:00.84,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,we're going to look at Episodes 7 and 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:05.20,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,This is an AfterTalk, so I'll be doing a lot of talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:06.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,Since I'll be chatting away,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.84,0:18:14.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,if you find me too noisy, please go back and watch the scenes in the game later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:15.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,Okay, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.20,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Episodes 7 and 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:18.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.00,0:33:36.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,She's... calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.68,0:33:39.72,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I think she knew deep down all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.72,0:33:41.64,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Wait, was her account hacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.64,0:33:42.14,Default,host,0,0,0,,Oh, it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.76,0:33:46.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,This is Ena after making so many resolutions and steeling herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.52,0:33:47.31,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.31,0:33:48.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.72,0:33:52.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,That account for her selfies...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.00,0:33:56.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,Those selfies were a bit of an escape for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.28,0:33:57.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,something she relied on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.68,0:33:59.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,But she couldn't run away anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.20,0:34:01.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,She even went to the Peach Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.52,0:34:08.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,But she still lacked the confidence to tell those around her or even fully commit herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.60,0:34:11.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,In this story,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.04,0:34:17.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,she was finally able to truly make up her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.99,0:34:20.66,Default,host,0,0,0,,That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.66,0:34:31.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's painful from here on, but there's a sense of relief, like the fog in her heart has cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.04,0:34:37.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,I put all those complex feelings into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.88,0:34:47.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,and I acted the final scenes while thinking about how Ena must feel relieved too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.56,0:35:05.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,The reason I chose Episodes 7 and 8 is because of her father. They've been through a lot and there were times she couldn't face him, but she really does admire him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.50,0:35:42.74,Default,host,0,0,0,,Her father isn't great with words, and Ena had hidden her respect for him behind her own frustration. But as she grew as an artist, she remembered those feelings. I also got to voice young Ena, who was so pure and saw the world as something sparkling and new, with her father right there in the middle of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.74,0:35:49.38,Default,host,0,0,0,,To her, her father was someone she looked up to,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.38,0:35:52.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,someone who could create incredible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.12,0:35:55.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,He was like a mass of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.88,0:36:02.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,I acted while keeping that image of talking to someone like that in mind, feeling the greatness of the art he creates.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.44,0:36:17.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,Because I performed with that sparkle in my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.12,0:39:05.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,there were many scenes where she's told she can keep painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.32,0:39:10.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,I performed those scenes without many breaks, just letting the emotions flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.08,0:39:12.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,The scenery she saw with her father, the voice of her father...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.40,0:39:21.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,It wasn't just about being held; it was about Ena finally being able to enjoy painting. Seeing her way of life reach everyone meant a lot to me personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.68,0:39:24.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm so happy that people are pleased and feel like they've been given a push forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.64,0:39:27.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,Some said it made them want to do their best too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.24,0:39:32.14,Default,host,0,0,0,,For those who have been supporting Ena all this time, she's finally reached a point on her journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.14,0:39:34.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm so glad she finally made it here. But it's only just beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.88,0:39:36.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,Still, there were so many emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.40,0:39:37.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm so moved by Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.20,0:39:42.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,It makes me so happy that everyone could empathize with her feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.28,0:39:43.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,Truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.04,0:39:49.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,Actually, when I first saw the script, I burst into tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.24,0:39:49.75,Default,host,0,0,0,,While reading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.75,0:39:51.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I could give it my all in the performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.16,0:39:52.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.12,0:39:53.70,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm just so glad it's out there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.70,0:39:54.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,That's how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.04,0:39:55.40,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.40,0:39:56.21,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.21,0:39:58.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,Looking at the illustrations, the core of Ena's journey...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.40,0:40:02.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,is that she's been facing her art for years. It's not just that she likes it; she's suffered and struggled with many emotions while continuing to paint.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.88,0:40:06.90,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I think many of you found it easy to empathize with the moment in the story where a glimmer of hope finally appeared for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.90,0:40:07.60,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,That's how I feel, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.48,0:40:08.15,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.15,0:40:11.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,Now, since we have about four minutes left,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.44,0:40:15.26,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'd like for us to take a look at the card illustrations together.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.26,0:40:18.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,Before we look at the art, the illustration team, who understands Ena's feelings so well,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.32,0:40:22.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,provided some comments about the costume Ena worked so hard for. Let me introduce those.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.28,0:40:26.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,This time, it's about Ena's struggle to get into art school...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.52,0:40:28.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,Saying she's "rewarded" might be too simple, but it's about her moving forward through that struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.80,0:40:30.06,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.06,0:40:34.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,The theme of the story was about facing a setback when her skills didn't reach the required level,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.28,0:40:37.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,but still not giving up. When I first read the script, I really felt that core theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.16,0:40:41.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,The design motif is a school uniform with a personal apron for painting. Congratulations to Suzuki for the production!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.44,0:40:45.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,The design was made to look like an art student's style during their entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.00,0:40:47.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,As a style for Ena as a painter, it feels like she's finally made it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.84,0:40:52.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,While the outfit for this event is simple, the apron is made of patchwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.32,0:40:56.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,This represents her standing tall and persevering even after nearly giving up many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.80,0:40:58.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's a design with unique touches,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.44,0:41:00.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,almost like things are finally coming together. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.88,0:41:01.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,I need a lot of tissues... Here's the sailor collar.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.20,0:41:06.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,They kept elements of the school uniform, like the collar and pleats, to leave a strong impression,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.72,0:41:07.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,but added a tear-shaped arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.84,0:41:09.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,They were very conscious of making it feel like a proper costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.36,0:41:11.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,Seeing that in the illustration and the acting... it really comes through.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.68,0:41:12.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,It really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.48,0:41:18.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,Playing Ena... and then seeing the Training After version... the reaction from everyone was huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.52,0:41:19.62,Default,host,0,0,0,,I was crying while recording,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.62,0:41:22.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,and Ena is crying while she paints too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.48,0:41:23.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,Her hands are all dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.76,0:41:25.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's so moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.36,0:41:29.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,And to all of you who watched over Ena and pressed the button to support her,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.84,0:41:31.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,helping her move forward to the next step...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.16,0:41:36.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,The time leading up to that button press, both before and after training, is truly precious. Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.76,0:41:40.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm just so grateful and moved. As someone on the creative side,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.24,0:41:43.16,Default,host,0,0,0,,I had so many thoughts about this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.16,0:41:46.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,Even though the genre is different, I felt I could really understand Ena's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.84,0:41:54.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,And Kaito... Kaito-san gave Ena so many important words.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.92,0:41:58.52,Default,host,0,0,0,,They even eat ice cream together, so please check that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.52,0:42:01.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,I called it "Yogurt Ice Cream" in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.36,0:42:04.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,That's because I personally love yogurt ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.00,0:42:04.71,Default,host,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.71,0:42:06.06,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's like, "Wait, it's just your preference?"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.06,0:42:07.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,And then there's Miku-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.84,0:42:08.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.68,0:42:10.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,What a lovely picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.12,0:42:12.98,Default,host,0,0,0,,She's eating ice cream too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.98,0:42:13.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.97,0:42:15.47,Default,host,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.52,0:42:19.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,And Mafuyu...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.36,0:42:22.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,If you long-press...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.44,0:42:23.03,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.68,0:42:25.08,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,She's holding an apron.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.08,0:42:26.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.16,0:42:29.66,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.66,0:42:34.74,Default,host,0,0,0,,So, we've looked at the illustrations for before and after training.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.74,0:42:36.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,Oh man, how many times have I done this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.60,0:42:38.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.56,0:42:45.38,Default,host,0,0,0,,I can talk about the story for a few more minutes, so I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.38,0:42:50.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,Regarding the previous story... well,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.68,0:42:52.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,how should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.56,0:42:54.80,Default,host,0,0,0,,It wasn't specifically about her art.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.80,0:43:01.96,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Before that, I sang the song "I am Rain."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.96,0:43:05.42,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,When we had a story about Ena's art—I don't like saying "drawings"—
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.42,0:43:12.60,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,when we had a story about her art, I happened to go to a museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.60,0:43:19.88,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I was able to act while keeping in mind what it means to look at a painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.88,0:43:24.72,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,To get to know Ena better... this time, I happened to be walking down a street,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.72,0:43:31.94,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,and there was a school that people aiming for art school probably attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.94,0:43:33.76,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I thought, "So this is what it's like."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.76,0:43:46.30,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Even just looking from the outside, I felt a great sense of tension. I recorded my lines while realizing how tough of an environment she's in.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.30,0:43:57.58,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I try to act every day in a way that conveys the atmosphere of the place where Ena is to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.58,0:43:58.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.44,0:44:07.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,So, we have a few dozen seconds left.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.76,0:44:13.02,Default,host,0,0,0,,By now, some of you might have already seen the AfterLive.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.02,0:44:17.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,Since it takes place after the story,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.60,0:44:22.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,you can see Ena's refreshed face. Things will still be hard from here on out,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.48,0:44:27.32,Default,host,0,0,0,,but you can see in her expression that she's truly made her decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.32,0:44:34.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'd be happy if my voice and the song are reaching you all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.91,0:44:35.41,Default,host,0,0,0,,Truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.95,0:44:36.45,Default,host,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.20,0:44:39.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,It's such a good story. Ena...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.36,0:44:41.54,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,...is truly loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.54,0:44:43.62,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I'm so grateful for such a wonderful story.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.62,0:44:50.14,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,With that said, let's talk about the song after we watch the 3DMV created for this event.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.14,0:44:51.92,Default,host,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.88,0:45:11.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,Breathing within a borrowed life and a body that can't become anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.04,0:45:21.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,If I dive deep inside, the me from that day I started drawing...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.48,0:45:26.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,...is still smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.48,0:45:41.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,Looking back, it's certainly there,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.08,0:45:47.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,the dream that had sprouted in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.68,0:45:53.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,Crushed by the shadow of ideals,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.24,0:46:08.20,Default,host,0,0,0,,it's no use stroking a past that eventually turned into hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.92,0:46:14.40,Default,host,0,0,0,,This small, gentle,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.12,0:46:19.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,belief hasn't reached yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.76,0:46:23.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,Even so, parched,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.20,0:46:28.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,the pure white scenery before my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.12,0:46:33.36,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'll try to paint more of the future with these hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.88,0:46:41.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,Even if it's not beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.20,0:46:44.24,Default,host,0,0,0,,in my own way,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.60,0:46:49.72,Default,host,0,0,0,,just what I see,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.84,0:46:55.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,I will keep painting this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.64,0:47:06.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,And there we go... sorry, my screen just cut out.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.56,0:47:15.76,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,The title of the song written for this event is being revealed for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.16,0:47:19.16,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,The title is 'The Name of That Painting'.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.16,0:47:21.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,That was the 3DMV.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.52,0:47:22.04,Default,host,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.72,0:47:26.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,Wait, I have it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.32,0:47:33.08,Default,host,0,0,0,,For a second, I thought my own notes were Chouchou-P's comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.08,0:47:33.60,Default,host,0,0,0,,My mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.60,0:47:38.88,Default,host,0,0,0,,These are the notes I sent to the staff beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.88,0:47:39.80,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I'll read them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.56,0:47:46.08,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Just listening to it makes me feel Ena's journey, and it brings me to tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.64,0:47:51.28,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,The title contains the characters for 'painting' and 'Na' from her name,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.28,0:47:53.92,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,so it really feels like a song written specifically for Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.80,0:48:00.44,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Rather than just being pessimistic about regrets, frustration, and pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.44,0:48:08.10,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I sang this with her resolve to turn those feelings into strength and the positive outlook she gained from that resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.10,0:48:11.00,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,That's what the past me emailed to the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.72,0:48:16.68,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,As for Chouchou-P's comments, they've been introduced on the ProSeka Station and such,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.68,0:48:20.56,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,and I think they're on Twitter—or X—so please check them out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.12,0:48:24.28,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Yes, those were the feelings I put into the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.80,0:48:31.36,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,There are lyrics that feel like she's looking back at the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.36,0:48:35.04,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,but it feels like the current Ena is the one doing the reflecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.76,0:48:40.00,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Ena definitely has regrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.00,0:48:50.28,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,but she's a girl who understands that those regrets made her who she is today. So even for the phrases looking back,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.28,0:48:57.44,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I didn't want to sing them with total agonizing pain. I kept that in mind while recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.96,0:49:03.16,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Like I said earlier, she's found her resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.16,0:49:10.76,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I sang with that sense of relief and the bright feeling of finally understanding, while keeping the story in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.76,0:49:15.44,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,But this isn't the goal; it's a new start.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.44,0:49:24.54,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I tried to capture that middle-ground feeling while singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.54,0:49:36.68,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,So, rather than a huge explosion of emotion, it's more like quietly reciting the words within myself to spur me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.68,0:49:40.32,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Like I'm patting my own chest and telling myself to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.32,0:49:46.28,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I sang it with that kind of self-encouragement in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.28,0:49:48.64,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I guess I really am going to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.56,0:49:52.10,Default,host,0,0,0,,I can hear the full version...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.10,0:49:53.50,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm the one who sang it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.50,0:49:54.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.68,0:49:57.00,Default,host,0,0,0,,I'm tearing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.00,0:49:58.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,I just can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.76,0:50:02.02,Default,host,0,0,0,,Both this story and the song just make me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.02,0:50:03.66,Default,host,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.66,0:50:06.48,Default,host,0,0,0,,I really thought I wouldn't cry this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.48,0:50:07.44,Default,host,0,0,0,,but here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.00,0:50:08.90,Default,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.90,0:50:14.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,To those of you who were a bit jealous that I get to hear the full version...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.12,0:50:15.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.64,0:50:27.58,Default,host,0,0,0,,The 2DMV for this new song, 'The Name of That Painting', will be uploaded to the official ProSeka YouTube channel at 22:15.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.58,0:50:31.68,Default,host,0,0,0,,Please check that out along with the 3DMV.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.68,0:50:34.04,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,So that means you'll be able to hear the full version too.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.04,0:50:36.48,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I hope the 2D MV is as great as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.16,0:50:40.56,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I haven't seen the 2DMV myself yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.56,0:50:45.68,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It's a bit late, but regarding my thoughts on the 3DMV...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.68,0:50:50.52,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We recorded the full version originally,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.52,0:50:54.38,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,and the lines are distributed, so I wondered which parts would be Ena's.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.38,0:50:59.58,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,The song starts with the other three members of Niigo in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.58,0:51:06.90,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,In the 3DMV in my head, I thought, 'Oh, it's not Ena?'
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.90,0:51:09.68,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I was wondering how it would start.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.68,0:51:14.30,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I wondered if all four or five of them would just pop onto the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.30,0:51:18.62,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I thought it would start with Mizuki since they sing the first line, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.62,0:51:23.28,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Ena was on screen the whole time. Of course, because of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.28,0:51:32.56,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I'm sure fans of other characters are happy when their favorites get more screen time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.56,0:51:36.38,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,But this MV really put the spotlight on Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.38,0:51:46.28,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It matches the story so well, and I felt like the MV really captured Ena's way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.28,0:51:51.20,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,As Ena's voice actress, that made me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.24,0:51:59.36,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Her art is always featured, but the songs for Ena's stories...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.36,0:52:05.08,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,The setting feels like it's gradually moving closer to the surface, and I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.08,0:52:08.92,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Well, that's just my own geeky theory, but it makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.92,0:52:15.20,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I've only seen it a few times myself, so I want to take a closer look later.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.20,0:52:17.68,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I'm so excited for the 2D MV.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.68,0:52:18.31,Default,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.48,0:52:20.14,Default,host,0,0,0,,I think that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.14,0:52:22.76,Default,host,0,0,0,,I don't think I have anything left to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.76,0:52:28.10,Default,host,0,0,0,,Not really, but I've put everything into Ena's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.10,0:52:37.68,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I've entrusted it all to her, so more than anything, I hope you can feel Ena's way of life through the song and story.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.28,0:52:41.66,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Everyone, please keep supporting Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.66,0:52:44.68,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,To everyone who supports her, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.68,0:52:48.26,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I'm not Ena myself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.26,0:53:09.86,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,As her voice actress, I like to think I'm close to her. She's made a new resolution, and I'll do my best to express her growth as an actress, so please keep an eye on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.86,0:53:11.30,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.30,0:53:15.08,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It's been a short time, but that's all for ProSeka AfterTalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.64,0:53:38.02,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,You can read the whole event story in the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.02,0:53:39.56,Default,host,0,0,0,,so please check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.56,0:53:43.70,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,We're always looking for messages for AfterTalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.70,0:53:51.86,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,You can send them via the AfterTalk channel on the official ProSeka Discord or by email.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.86,0:53:56.82,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Please send one in when the next AfterTalk event is held.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.82,0:54:00.60,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,Please make sure your messages are related to the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.60,0:54:03.67,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,It'd be a waste if they didn't get read because they were off-topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.67,0:54:04.42,Default,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.42,0:54:08.12,Default,host,0,0,0,,So, it's almost time. In just a few dozen seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.12,0:54:12.96,Default,host,0,0,0,,The 2D MV will be out, so let's watch it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.96,0:54:18.14,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,I'll watch it as soon as I close this stream, so you all should watch it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.14,0:54:21.54,Default,listener_mail,0,0,0,,With that, I'll see you all again.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.54,0:54:23.84,Default,host,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.56,0:54:40.28,Default,host,0,0,0,,Oh, I still have time?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.28,0:54:40.99,Default,host,0,0,0,,Um...
